# HNG Stage 3 — Anomaly Detection Engine

A real-time DDoS detection and automated response daemon built alongside Nextcloud on Docker.

## Live Links

| Resource | URL |
|----------|-----|
| Metrics Dashboard | http://hnglani.duckdns.org:8080 |
| Server IP | 52.91.81.234 |
